{"tid":2180210,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"英語母語者黎香港做小學NET易唔易比人請","createTime":"2020-08-29T16:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T00:45:10.000Z","uid":370862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"56eda207bcac85cd281548478723aedd7433a231","tid":2180210,"uid":370862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"我見教育局有詳細寫要求/條件，唔係個個cat都要求一定有教育文憑<br />\n想知道如果係英美土生土長既大學畢業生，其實黎香港做小學NET易唔易<br />\n話哂都pt15-29 (冇教育文憑bar at 20)，成3皮起薪，應該係好多西方國家做老師都未必有<br />\n好似都幾吸引...(假設冇住屋問題)<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係做教育局資助位，一般人工又有幾多？"},{"pid":"bdb8da068c56b73ea9cdda0d7f958fc1d5af16d6","tid":2180210,"uid":26071,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:24:52.000Z","msg":"NET唔係白人就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界永遠最racist係Asian自己"},{"pid":"02151ca4dedfd748d028c71d239f170dcb67d3fe","tid":2180210,"uid":38316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"我以前教會中學個NET係印度人，同一時間教埋西史<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ac480f9ff63636cfb5241c88e63e79742a6534","tid":2180210,"uid":370862,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb8da068c56b73ea9cdda0d7f958fc1d5af16d6","tid":2180210,"uid":26071,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:24:52.000Z","msg":"NET唔係白人就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界永遠最racist係Asian自己"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"如果係白人呢？<br />\n諗起之前教育局流出個份潛條件，只請白人/女性，有D講到明唔請黑人...痴線"},{"pid":"c052f06c97de6993a3e289d3fec01bee297f8e1a","tid":2180210,"uid":181233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"應該都幾易<br />\n識兩個英國白人degree都唔係education，但係都做到小學NET"},{"pid":"30f3e5862c9820a962381e600f431786564cf5d7","tid":2180210,"uid":11966,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"bdb8da068c56b73ea9cdda0d7f958fc1d5af16d6","ti